OL,3,CRow over MP's claim street blighted by
OL,4,Cillegal immigrants
OL,6,FAfter being elected said she had
OL,7,Freceived "disturbing reports" from
OL,8,Fpeople who wanted to remain anonymous
OL,9,Fabout incidents at houses of multiple
OL,10,Foccupation (HMOs) on Greenway Road,
OL,11,FRuncorn.
OL,13,FIn a video she said: "There are HMOs
OL,14,Fon this road with illegal immigrants
OL,15,Fin it.
OL,17,F"The anti-social behaviour that people
OL,18,Fhave to put up with, the noise levels,
OL,19,Fthe violence, the rubbish strewn
OL,20,Faround the street and the police have
OL,21,Fbeen called and they don't come out."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
