OL,3,CRow over MP's claim street blighted by
OL,4,Cillegal immigrants
OL,6,FBut, the claim has been disputed by
OL,7,Fneighbours like Jaki Florek, who has
OL,8,Flived there since the 1980s.
OL,10,F"It's a really pleasant, nice area to
OL,11,Flive in," she said. "Every word Sarah
OL,12,FPochin said in her video, it's just
OL,13,Fridiculously not true."
OL,15,FHer son Joe added: "That kind of
OL,16,Flanguage, it's incitive, it's
OL,17,Fdivisive, it's just not true."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
