OL,3,CRow over MP's claim street blighted by
OL,4,Cillegal immigrants
OL,6,FOther residents also defended the
OL,7,Farea. "There's never been any trouble,
OL,8,Fyou don't see any police around here
OL,9,Ffor any of these HMOs," Julie Collins-
OL,10,FPower said.
OL,12,FBut the MP said, although she has
OL,13,Freceived a lot of push back, she was
OL,14,Fnot surprised because she was raising
OL,15,Fissues which a lot of people did not
OL,16,Fwant to hear.
OL,18,F"I'm raising a lot of issues people
OL,19,Fdon't want to hear, that they're in
OL,20,Fdenial about.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
