OL,6,F"But I'm raising them for the
OL,7,Fconstituents who come to me with these
OL,8,Fissues that are causing them problems
OL,9,Fin their day to day lives," she said.
OL,11,F"They don't go to the police because
OL,12,Fpeople are too scared to go to the
OL,13,Fpolice."
OL,15,FDefending her use of the term, illegal
OL,16,Fimmigrants, she added: "Anybody who
OL,17,Fcomes here illegally is breaking the
OL,18,Flaw. I stand by illegal immigrants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
