OL,6,F"What I am raising here are local
OL,7,Fissues of antisocial behaviour and
OL,8,Fconcern about domestic violence and
OL,9,Feverything else I've talked about."
OL,11,FCheshire Police said the issues raised
OL,12,Fdidn't correlate with those raised to
OL,13,Fofficers - adding that police had
OL,14,Fattended just one incident of domestic
OL,15,Fviolence at an HMO on Greenway Road in
OL,16,Fjust six months, no arrest was made.
OL,18,FHalton Council said no issues had been
OL,19,Fraised to them in the past 12 months.
